    "Memories are where your tickets come together. Group them by trip, event, or place — whatever you want to remember." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Erinnerungen sammeln deine Tickets an einem Ort — eine Reise, eine Saison, eine Nacht. Alles, was du bewahren möchtest."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Memories gather tickets into one place — a trip, a season, a night out. Whatever you want to hold onto."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Las memorias reúnen tus tickets en un solo lugar — un viaje, una temporada, una noche. Lo que quieras guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les souvenirs regroupent vos billets en un seul endroit — un voyage, une saison, une soirée. Tout ce que vous voulez garder."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "I ricordi riuniscono i biglietti in un unico posto — un viaggio, una stagione, una serata. Quello che vuoi tenere stretto."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "メモリーはチケットを一箇所にまとめます — 旅、季節、夜。心に残したいものを。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "추억은 티켓을 한 곳에 모읍니다 — 여행, 계절, 어느 밤. 간직하고 싶은 모든 것을."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "回忆把您的门票聚在一处——一次旅行、一个季节、一个夜晚。任何想珍藏的瞬间。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
