    "The toggles below won't take effect until you enable notifications for Lumoria in iOS Settings. Tap to open." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the effect of toggling notifications.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aktiviere zuerst Benachrichtigungen für Lumoria in den Einstellungen — danach greifen die Schalter unten. Tippe, um zu öffnen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Turn notifications on for Lumoria in Settings first — the toggles below will take effect after that. Tap to open."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Primero activa las notificaciones para Lumoria en Ajustes — después los interruptores de abajo surtirán efecto. Toca para abrir."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Activez d’abord les notifications pour Lumoria dans les Réglages — ensuite, les interrupteurs ci-dessous prendront effet. Touchez pour ouvrir."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Prima attiva le notifiche per Lumoria in Impostazioni — dopo gli interruttori qui sotto avranno effetto. Tocca per aprire."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "まず iOS の設定で Lumoria の通知をオンにしてください。下のスイッチはそのあと有効になります。タップして開きます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "먼저 설정에서 Lumoria 알림을 켜 주세요. 아래 토글은 그 뒤에 적용됩니다. 탭하여 열기."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "先在 iOS 设置中为 Lumoria 打开通知 — 下方开关才会生效。点按即可前往。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This info doesn't need to be accurate — you're not making a real ticket. Only airport codes must be real, to draw the path." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nichts davon muss echt sein — es geht bei diesen Tickets um das Gefühl, nicht um den Flug. Verwende nur echte Flughafencodes, damit wir die Route auf der Karte anzeigen können."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "None of this needs to be real — these tickets are about the feeling, not the flight. Just use real airport codes so we can place the route on the map."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nada de esto tiene que ser real — estos tickets son sobre la sensación, no sobre el vuelo. Usa códigos de aeropuerto reales para que podamos colocar la ruta en el mapa."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Rien de tout cela n’a besoin d’être réel — ces billets, c’est l’émotion qui compte, pas le vol. Utilisez simplement de vrais codes d’aéroport pour que nous puissions placer le trajet sur la carte."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nulla di tutto questo deve essere reale — questi biglietti parlano della sensazione, non del volo. Usa solo codici aeroportuali reali così possiamo tracciare il tragitto sulla mappa."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "どれも実際のものでなくて大丈夫 — このチケットは「フライト」ではなく「気分」のためのもの。空港コードだけは本物を使ってください、地図上にルートを表示できるように。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "전부 실제일 필요는 없어요 — 이 티켓은 비행 그 자체가 아니라 그 순간의 느낌에 관한 것입니다. 공항 코드만 실제 값을 사용해 주세요, 그래야 지도에 경로를 표시할 수 있어요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些信息不必真实 — 这些门票是关于那份心情，而不是那趟航班。只需填入真实的机场代码，我们就能把航线标在地图上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
